Looking closer at the contraption you can see that it is a long, rectangular
box with numerous broken windows in its side. It also has six metal wheels,
in three groups of two, attached to its bottom side. The faint breeze in
the tunnel rustles the webs that partially hide an opening leading inside.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MONSTER_GROUP 103
IFENTRY
 IFITEM 5
