PARTIAL_DARKNESS
INDOOR_GROUND
MONSTER_GROUP 16
*DESCRIPTION_START
Lurid moans echo through this chamber, chilling enough to send shivers
running up and down the spine. The smell of rotting flesh and disease
overpowers the musty smells of the bare earthen walls. Roots protrude
from hastily dug walls, and clumps of dirt fall to the floor every few
seconds. Apart from the noise and smell, the room is devoid of any
furnishings, and the only items of interest are the three exits.
One is the trapdoor in the ceiling of the chamber, and the other
two are passages going east and northwest.
*DESCRIPTION_END
