NUMBER 574
NAME Kvantar Underground
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
INDOOR_GROUND
MONSTER_GROUP 16
*DESCRIPTION_START
This large, circular room contains the rotting remains of humanoids, probably
chained to the walls of the chamber while alive. Now are all in various stages
of decomposition. On some, that are for the most part, "fresh," one can see
where various pieces have been sliced off, as if they were slabs of meat
hanging in a butcher's meat locker. Strangely enough, out of all the bodies
in the room there is only one that is totally stripped of flesh. The
remainder have at least some rotting remnant of flesh left, be it an
eyeball hanging loosely from an empty eye socket, or green pus covered
tissue hanging from a rib. The skeleton is flesh free and covered by
cobwebs, forgotten by both the Kvantar and time itself. There is a
wooden door in the east wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 573
