FIXED_LIGHT
NAME Pristine Forest
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in the clearing of a vast forest. Giant, thick trees form impassible
barriers all around you. A fantastic mountain panorama provides a majestic
backdrop. Within the depths of the forest, you hear a number of sounds: the
croaking of toads, the calls of birds, the babbling of a distant brook. For
some reason, you feel at peace here. On your side to the west, two gnarled
trees form an archway from which emanates a cool, blue glow. In the center
of the clearing, a door leads into a quaint cabin.
*DESCRIPTION_END
item 0 60 val2=201
item 1 66 val1=100 val2=93 val3=19993 unlocked
