FIXED_LIGHT
FORGE
NAME Cabin
*DESCRIPTION_START
The warm interior of the cabin greets you with rugged simplicity. Panelled in dark hard woods, the walls and floor shimmer and shift hypnotically beneath the flickering yellow light of oil lamps affixed throughout the room. The sweet scent of cured grass fills the air, wafted down from a coarsly thatched ceiling to mask the gritty smell of hot steel and burning coal. In one corner, murky tendrils of smoke rise away from the glowing red coals of a small sandstone forge, and out the opening above.
*DESCRIPTION_END
