NUMBER 973
NAME Cavern, terminus
*DESCRIPTION_START
There are gashes in the walls at this end of the cavern and marks that appear to have been made by primitive tools. It is obvious that some agent has partially removed the rock walls and enlarged the cavern. A few stones, chiselled into bricks and cubes, lie scattered around. The stream gurgles and disappears into a fissure near the southern wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
CAVE
MINEC
DARKNESS
EXIT N 972
MONSTER_GROUP 24
