NAME Caverns, recesses
*DESCRIPTION_START
The walls of this small chamber are wet and filled with darkened recesses. Uncounted centuries of mineral-laden drippings have caused delicate blue and green stalactites and stalagmites to fuse over each opening like bars on tiny windows.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 959
CAVE
MINEC
DARKNESS
MONSTER_GROUP 25
;
ITEM 0 363
ITEM 1 368
