*DESCRIPTION_START
Waves gently lap over a large, rusted anchor stuck in the sand at the water's edge. A thick chain leads into the sea from the anchor. The anchor, judging by its worn condition, has been sitting here for some time. The relentless waves have exposed an opening in the rocks which leads down into darkness.
*DESCRIPTION_END
