NUMBER 963
NAME Caverns, west chasm
*DESCRIPTION_START
A huge crevice slashes the tunnel. Smooth walls extend out of sight both up and down, left and right. Stone posts on either side of the chasm may have been part of a bridge that has since disintegrated. An opening on the far side beckons, but a difficult jump seems to be the only chance of reaching it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 962
CAVE
MINEC
DARKNESS
MONSTER_GROUP 25
;
ITEM 0 331
;chasm
;
IFVERB JUMP 0
	RANDOM CHANCE 1 100
	ADD CHANCE AGI
	IFVAR CHANCE < 81
		ECHO PLAYER You cannot quite muster the courage to attempt the jump.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR CHANCE > 80
		IFVAR CHANCE < 130
			ECHO OTHERS %N makes a mighty leap to cross the chasm but misses andfalls into the darkness below!%c
			ECHO PLAYER You make a mighty leap to cross the chasm but you can't quite make it and fall!%c
			ECHO PLAYER As you tumble head over heels, your life flashes, too short, before your eyes and you wonder how deep "bottomless" is.%c
			DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 50 Miraculously, you land with a thud, on a tiny ledge.
			MOVE 966
			AFFECT 964
			ECHO OTHERS %N jumps from the other side of the chasm but misses and falls into the darkness below!
			AFFECT 966
			ECHO OTHERS %N, falling from above, lands with ungracefully beside you.
			AFFECT 963
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR CHANCE => 130
		ECHO OTHERS %N makes a heroic leap across the chasm and lands safely on the other side!
		ECHO PLAYER You fling yourself confidently over the chasm and land safely on the other side!
		MOVE 964
		AFFECT 964
		ECHO OTHERS %n jumps the chasm from the other side and lands safely beside you.
		AFFECT 963
	ENDIF
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
;
