*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
Pieces of carved stone lie everywhere, the neck of a swan here, the leg of a man there and, in the center, powdered remains of something that was more than casually demolished.
*DESCRIPTION_END
