This room contains a large, round table of oak surrounded by ten enamelled chairs, each gilt with a slightly different decorative design. On the walls hang rotting and burnt shreds of cloth, all that remain of tapestries of great craftsmanship. There is a black enamelled door to the east.
*DESCRIPTION_END
