		ECHO PLAYER You feel the muscles in your face relaxing, loosening.
		PLREVENT 5
		CONTPLREVENT
			ECHO PLAYER You feel as one with the universe...
			RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 200
			SHOWROOM DUMMY1
		PLREVENT 5
